{"tid":2425553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武裝劫獄致最少25死，包括監獄獄長！","createTime":"2021-02-27T12:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T14:39:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f19e640ab75660b7f1fba0181eaab75a015ff4bd","tid":2425553,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:01:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577847-20210227.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577847-20210227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=95a95c80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577847-20210227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c0960744\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577847-20210227.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n海地一所監獄發生騷亂，當局說最少25人死亡，400多名犯人越獄。<br />\n<br />\n事發監獄位於首都太子港市郊。官員說死亡的25人，包括監獄獄長及6名犯人，其餘是當地居民；部分越獄犯人已經被捕，當局正調查事發原因。總統莫伊茲譴責越獄事件，呼籲民眾冷靜，又說已下令警方採取一切行動控制形勢。<br />\n<br />\n一批武裝分子在當地星期四，襲擊監獄保安人員，部分犯人乘機逃跑。報道說，事件可能與當地犯罪集團，試圖接走被關押的頭目有關。監獄共關押超過1500名犯人，遠超設計的承載能力。"},{"pid":"8d7cd1fae5418d49cd6a74951c542f7608f0c3ac","tid":2425553,"uid":30084,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:22:08.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 好撚暴力 <br />\n<br />\n點解唔夾錢捐俾海地612 用黎打官司<br />\n<br />\n同搞海地經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n咁暴力劫獄<br />\n<br />\n要相信法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n犯法點得架"},{"pid":"2421474c6189f972f9c1e3bbf3ea92f29cea067a","tid":2425553,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8d7cd1fae5418d49cd6a74951c542f7608f0c3ac","tid":2425553,"uid":30084,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:22:08.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 好撚暴力 <br />\n<br />\n點解唔夾錢捐俾海地612 用黎打官司<br />\n<br />\n同搞海地經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n咁暴力劫獄<br />\n<br />\n要相信法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj